Feature 1: Email Forwarding
- Feature Name: Email Forwarding
- Description: This feature allows users to forward emails to other recipients.
- Key Functionality: Capability to forward received emails to another email address. Ability to set up rules for automatic forwarding of emails.
- User Benefit: Users can easily share important information or relevant emails with others, ensuring efficient communication and collaboration.

Feature 2: Email Filtering
- Feature Name: Email Filtering
- Description: This feature enables users to filter incoming emails based on specific criteria.
- Key Functionality: Ability to set up filters to automatically categorize emails based on sender, subject, keywords, or other criteria. Organizing emails into folders based on filtering rules.
- User Benefit: Users can prioritize and manage incoming emails more effectively, reducing clutter and enabling quicker access to important messages.

Feature 3: Email Scheduling
- Feature Name: Email Scheduling
- Description: This feature allows users to schedule emails to be sent at a later time.
- Key Functionality: Capability to compose emails and schedule them for sending at a specified date and time. Ability to delay sending an email for a specific period of time.
- User Benefit: Users can plan their communications in advance, ensuring timely delivery of messages and facilitating better time management.

Feature 4: Email Templates
- Feature Name: Email Templates
- Description: This feature enables users to save email templates for repetitive messages.
- Key Functionality: Ability to create, save, and reuse predefined email templates for common messages. Easily insert variables into email templates for personalized messages.
- User Benefit: Users can save time on composing recurring messages, maintain consistency in communication, and personalize emails efficiently.

Feature 5: Email Tracking
- Feature Name: Email Tracking
- Description: This feature allows users to track the status of their sent emails.
- Key Functionality: Capability to monitor when emails are opened by recipients and receive notifications for recipient interactions. Track email delivery status and engagement metrics.
- User Benefit: Users can gauge the effectiveness of their communications, follow up promptly when needed, and stay informed about recipient engagement with their emails.

