1. User Story: As a user, I want to be able to create a new account on the platform.

Engineering Tasks:
- Design the user interface for the account creation form.
- Implement backend logic to handle account creation requests.
- Implement frontend validation for user input.
- Write automated tests to verify account creation functionality.

2. User Story: As a user, I want to be able to search for products on the platform.

Engineering Tasks:
- Design the search bar UI component.
- Implement frontend logic to handle search queries.
- Develop backend API endpoints to handle search requests.
- Integrate search functionality with the existing product database.
- Write unit tests to ensure search functionality works as expected.

3. User Story: As a user, I want to be able to add products to my shopping cart.

Engineering Tasks:
- Design the shopping cart UI component.
- Implement frontend logic to add products to the cart.
- Update the backend to store cart information for each user.
- Implement functionalities to update and remove products from the cart.
- Write integration tests to verify the shopping cart functionality.

4. User Story: As a user, I want to be able to make a payment for my order.

Engineering Tasks:
- Design the payment form UI.
- Integrate a third-party payment gateway for processing payments.
- Implement frontend logic to handle payment submission.
- Update the backend to process payment requests and update order status.
- Write end-to-end tests to verify the payment process from start to finish.

